title: Chilliwack - Opus X (1982)
description:
From Wikipedia:
 
Opus X is the tenth album (hence the "X") by the Canadian rock band Chilliwack released in 1982. Producers Henderson and MacLeod received the Juno Award for "Producer of the Year" for their work on the songs "Whatcha Gonna Do" and "Secret Information" from this album.

Track listing:

All songs written by Bill Henderson & Brian MacLeod unless noted.

Don't It Make You Feel Good
Really Don't Mind
You're Gonna Last
Midnight
Whatcha Gonna Do
Secret Information (Henderson) 
She Don't Know
Night Time
Lean on Me
